{"tid":1520802,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"15歲前線嘅心聲 (續)","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T09:34:08.000Z","uid":146737,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5905340f52c0519be3a5d67965502f594368da27","tid":1520802,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsTQJ2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsTQJ2k.jpg&h=a40cc04a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n牆紙誓要對抗偏頗傳媒，<br />\n帶出真相！<br />\n<br />\n本「紙」秉承連儂牆原意，人人都可以投稿發表意見，等大眾嘅心聲可以多個機會比更多人知道，快啲貼晒喺全港既牆上啦！<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n暫定逢星期五出街，<br />\n講述過去一周發生的大事<br />\n同埋不同人士對呢場運動嘅睇法。<br />\n完整版嘅「牆紙」會貼係連儂牆上面<br />\n亦會有精華版係街頭派發。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">歡迎投稿 :<a href=\"https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Flennonnewshk%2F6g5yp3tllkxx&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2f3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c8257bd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2f3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=449259d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n第一期Link :<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link :<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"1e9c217445d9938124ff3211e4ccd83bc8e11f0b","tid":1520802,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces